Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31252596%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody-image%20disturbances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20stress-related%20disorders.%20Its%20use%20cases%20include%20trauma-focused%20therapy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mindfulness%20exercises%20and%20social-skills%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIncreased%20relaxation%20through%20immersive%20VR%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShel%20Mann%2C%20a%20cofounder%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20VR-development%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffireflyvr.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFireflyVR%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20VR%20could%20help%20open%20the%20brain's%20window%20of%20neuroplasticity%20and%20make%20it%20more%20receptive%20to%20relaxation%20and%20mindfulness%20practices%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20positive%20feelings%20and%20behaviors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMann%20said%20the%20company's%20research%20found%20that%20integrating%20biophysical%20signal%20recordings%2C%20such%20as%20patients'%20eye%20gaze%20and%20heart-rate%20variability%2C%20into%20immersive%20VR%20applications%20could%20enhance%20outcomes.%20Physiological%20responses%20offer%20reliable%20measures%20for%20assessing%20users'%20emotions%20and%20anxiety%20levels%2C%20which%20could%20revolutionize%20therapeutic%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20virtual-reality%20setting%20that%20shows%20a%20body%20of%20water%2C%20mountains%2C%20a%20forest%2C%20and%20sound%20bowls.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663249600dfb1341e90118f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20inside%20look%20at%20FireflyVR's%20tech%20shows%20how%20users%20can%20enter%20a%20peaceful%20virtual%20setting.%3Cp%3EFireflyVR%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Christopher%20Romig%2C%20the%20director%20of%20innovation%20at%20the%20mental-health%20clinic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstellacenter.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStella%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20uses%20FireflyVR%20tech%20to%20ease%20patients'%20anxiety%20before%20ketamine-infusion%20therapy%2C%20which%20is%20the%20intravenous%20administration%20of%20the%20drug.%20It's%20used%20to%20treat%20conditions%20such%20as%20depression%2C%20anxiety%2C%20and%20PTSD.%20The%20combination%20of%20ketamine%20and%20VR-guided%20therapy%2C%20he%20told%20BI%2C%20fosters%20neural%20connectivity%20at%20optimal%20brain-receptivity%20periods%20by%20helping%20calm%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVR%20is%20an%20engaging%20method%20for%20improving%20a%20patient's%20comfort%20and%20compliance%20during%20treatment%20sessions%2C%20Romig%20said.%20A%20patient's%20stress%20from%20their%20daily%20life%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20placed%20aside%20before%20they%20start%20their%20ketamine%20session%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20VR%2C%20setting%20intentions%2C%20and%20breath%20work%20are%20all%20very%20beneficial%20to%20helping%20ketamine%20establish%20the%20happy%2C%20healing%20pathways%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20uses%20FireflyVR's%20platform%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffireflyvr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2FEvidence-Based-Processes-Incorporated-in-The-Sanctuary.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Sanctuary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20clinically%20designed%20VR%20experience%20that%20uses%20cognitive-behavioral%20therapy%20to%20reduce%20patients'%20anxiety%20before%20they%20undergo%20ketamine%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20ketamine%20treatment%2C%20Romig%20said%2C%20patients%20enter%20%26quot%3Ba%20virtual%20world%20where%20they%20learn%20about%20setting%20intentions%2C%20letting%20go%2C%20ritual%20breathing%2C%20and%20creating%20positivity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20use%20it%20to%20create%20the%20'peaceful%20mind'%20for%20my%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20so%20many%20applications%2C%20and%20I%20think%20you'll%20see%20a%20lot%20more%20VR%20working%20its%20way%20into%20mental%20health%20in%20conjunction%20with%20biofeedback%20and%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223353%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20virtual-reality%20setting%20that%20shows%20a%20waterfall%20going%20into%20a%20lake%2C%20mountains%2C%20and%20a%20forest%20area.%20A%20prompt%20on%20the%20screen%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BConsider...What%20would%20I%20most%20like%20to%20change%20in%20my%20life%3F%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66324a270dfb1341e90119f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221868%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrompts%20can%20appear%20in%20FireflyVR's%20virtual%20environments%20to%20help%20patients%20practice%20mindfulness%20and%20set%20intentions.%3Cp%3EFireflyVR%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-therapy-mental-health-apps-betterhelp-talkspace-cerebral-dark-side-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental-health-care%20crisis%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20forward-thinking%20solutions%20are%20crucial.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20there's%20a%20shortage%20of%20therapists%2C%26quot%3B%20Mann%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20a%20nice-to-do%3B%20it's%20a%20need-to-do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sanctuary%20was%20adapted%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarketplace.va.gov%2Finnovations%2Fvalidation-of-the-sanctuary-vr-experience%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaddiction%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20the%20Veterans%20Affairs%20system.%20Mann%20said%20this%20was%20just%20one%20example%20of%20how%20the%20platform%20could%20be%20used.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20in%20VR%2C%20in%20an%20immersive%20setting%2C%20you're%20there.%20It%20really%20fools%20your%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20Mann%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20The%20Sanctuary%2C%20users%20learn%20about%20elements%20such%20as%20meditation%20and%20breathing%20techniques%2C%20allowing%20real-life%20therapists%20to%20focus%20their%20efforts%20more%20on%20the%20specifics%20of%20patients'%20diagnoses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EVR%20cue%20exposure%20and%20embodiment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20Siegfried%2C%20the%20chief%20clinical%20officer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flightfully.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELightfully%20Behavioral%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20uses%20VR%20for%20patients%20with%20eating%20disorders%20and%20body-image%20disturbances.%20Patients%20can%20use%20the%20VR%20tech%20in%20an%20office%20or%2C%20in%20some%20situations%2C%20take%20a%20VR%20device%20home%20and%20return%20it%20after%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVR%20cue%20exposure%2C%20Siegfried%20said%2C%20helps%20reduce%20binge-eating%20habits%20by%20exposing%20people%20to%20triggering%20stimuli%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment.%20Siegfried%20said%20cue%20exposure%20%26quot%3Bcan%20create%20a%20habituation%20to%20the%20cue%2C%20so%20when%20the%20client%20is%20confronted%20with%20the%20cue%20in%20real%20life%2C%20a%20binge%20is%20less%20probable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20VR%20allows%20people%20with%20a%20negative%20body%20image%20to%20see%20themselves%20with%20different%20body%20sizes%20in%20a%20safe%20space%20via%20embodiment.%20%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20is%20to%20decrease%20discomfort%20with%20weight%20gain%20in%20anorexia%2C%26quot%3B%20Siegfried%20said.%20The%20patient%20may%20experience%20increased%20acceptance%20of%20their%20appearance%20through%20repeated%20exposure%20via%20virtual%20simulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20cue%20exposure%20and%20embodiment%20aim%20to%20address%20the%20complex%20psychological%20dynamics%20of%20eating%20disorders.%20Siegfried%20emphasized%20VR's%20ability%20to%20immerse%20people%20in%20scenarios%20that%20are%20challenging%20to%20create%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20acts%20as%20a%20gateway%2C%20helping%20users%20overcome%20fears%20and%20challenges%20by%20digitally%20placing%20them%20in%20fraught%20scenarios.%20For%20instance%2C%20clients%20with%20panic%20disorder%20or%20agoraphobia%20can%20virtually%20leave%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20clients%20report%20a%20decrease%20in%20distress%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20willingness%20during%20the%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20Siegfried%20said.%20%26quot%3BBetween%20sessions%2C%20there%20is%20often%20a%20drift%20back%20toward%20baseline%2C%20which%20is%20why%20multiple%20sessions%20are%20necessary.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%20that%20these%20VR%20applications%20were%20%26quot%3Bmost%20effective%20as%20a%20step%20toward%20in%20vivo%20%E2%80%94%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20exposure.%26quot%3B%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20clients%20integrated%20into%20normality%20through%20exposure-based%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiegfried%20told%20BI%20that%20VR%20could%20also%20provide%20imaginal%20experiences%3A%20A%20burn%20victim%20could%20be%20virtually%20covered%20with%20snow%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20reduce%20pain%2C%20and%20someone%20who's%20afraid%20of%20flying%20could%20go%20through%20a%20simulation%20of%20traveling%20by%20flight%2C%20which%20could%20include%20arriving%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20checking%20in%2C%20landing%2C%20and%20picking%20up%20baggage.%20%26quot%3BThis%20simulation%20can%20be%20repeated%20until%20anxiety%20reduces%20and%20willingness%20increases%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Siegfried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20VR%20applications%20are%20relatively%20new%2C%20it%20might%20be%20difficult%20to%20find%20therapists%20who%20are%20adequately%20trained%20to%20effectively%20use%20the%20tech.%20Equipment%20can%20also%20be%20expensive%2C%20making%20some%20therapists%20reluctant%20to%20integrate%20VR%20use%20into%20their%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProgress%20is%20certainly%20underway%2C%20but%20it'll%20take%20more%20time%20for%20the%20technology%20to%20gain%20prevalence%20in%20mental-health%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22emb