20to%20stop%20building%20new%20coal%20plants%2C%20the%20dirtiest%20form%20of%20power%20production%2C%20because%20the%20expansion%20undercuts%20the%20country's%20promise%20that%20its%20greenhouse-gas%20emissions%20will%20start%20dropping%20after%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20moves%20by%20the%20US%20to%20connect%20the%20climate%20issue%20with%20trade%20measures%2C%20industrial%20competition%2C%20and%20national%20security%20is%20something%20I'm%20sure%20the%20Chinese%20will%20raise%20because%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20concerns%20on%20this%20policy%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Li%20Shuo%2C%20the%20director%20of%20China%20Climate%20Hub%20at%20the%20Asia%20Society%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%20said%20China's%20view%20was%20that%20the%20US%20prioritized%20economic%20competition%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20mitigating%20the%20climate%20emergency.%20The%20world%20needs%20affordable%20green%20technology%20for%20the%20energy%20transition%2C%20and%20China's%20record%20levels%20of%20investment%20have%20driven%20down%20the%20costs%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20example%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-chinese-automaker-byd-rose-to-challenge-tesla-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20the%20remarkable%20rise%20of%20BYD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Chinese%20automaker%20that%20briefly%20eclipsed%20Tesla%20this%20year%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20seller%20of%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20US%20views%20China%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20both%20national%20security%20and%20the%20climate.%20The%20country's%20boom%20in%20green-tech%20manufacturing%20was%20largely%20powered%20by%20dirty%20energy%2C%20with%20coal%20still%20accounting%20for%20about%2060%25%20of%20China's%20electricity%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spglobal.com%2Fcommodityinsights%2Fen%2Fmarket-insights%2Flatest-news%2Fenergy-transition%2F013124-coal-still-accounted-for-nearly-60-of-chinas-electricity-supply-in-2023-cec%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%20And%20even%20though%20China%20is%20adding%20renewable%20energy%20to%20its%20grid%20faster%20than%20any%20other%20country%2C%20it's%20also%20building%20new%20coal-fired%20power%20plants%20at%20a%20rapid%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoal%20is%20a%20major%20source%20of%20tension%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%2C%20Li%20said.%20China%20has%20no%20policy%20to%20signal%20a%20coal%20slowdown%2C%20undermining%20its%20climate%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20could%20be%20inflamed%20following%20a%20deal%20this%20week%20among%20seven%20of%20the%20world's%20wealthiest%20countries%20to%20stop%20burning%20coal%20for%20power%20by%202035.%20During%20a%20G7%20meeting%20in%20Italy%2C%20Japan%2C%20another%20major%20coal%20user%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g7italy.it%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FG7-Climate-Energy-Environment-Ministerial-Communique_Final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%20the%20timeline%20for%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20joined%20by%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20several%20European%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20the%20US%20in%20late%20April%20finalized%20stricter%20emissions%20limits%20on%20power%20plants%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20shift%20away%20from%20coal.%20About%2016%25%20of%20US%20electricity%20comes%20from%20coal%2C%20a%20steep%20drop%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20fracking%20boom%20that%20made%20gas%20a%20cheaper%20source%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20neither%20the%20US%20nor%20China%20is%20in%20a%20position%20to%20compromise%2C%20Li%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20defends%20its%20coal%20expansion%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20energy%20security.%20Last%20year%2C%20sky-high%20temperatures%20and%20drought%20in%20regions%20reliant%20on%20hydropower%20forced%20rolling%20blackouts%20and%20factory%20closures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden-administration%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20climate%20envoy%20John%20Podesta%20and%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Janet%20Yellen%2C%20in%20recent%20months%20have%20said%20the%20US%20is%20evaluating%20new%20strategies%20to%20counter%20China's%20dominance%20over%20green%20technology.%20Former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-impose-tariffs-china-if-elected-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20he%20would%20impose%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%2060%25%20on%20China%20if%20he%20won%20the%20election%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20tension%2C%20there%20likely%20won't%20be%20any%20major%20breakthroughs%20during%20this%20month's%20talks%2C%20Li%20said.%20But%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20polluters%20are%20meeting%20in%20person%20shows%20that%20the%20climate%20still%20carries%20special%20weight.%20Few%20Chinese%20senior%20officials%20travel%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-meeting-us-climate-solar-panels-coal-power-energy-security-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714657824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663397fdec0c696569001341%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-meeting-us-climate-solar-panels-coal-power-energy-security-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20meeting%20comes%20as%20the%20US%20and%20China%20jockey%20for%20power%20over%20renewable%20technology%20like%20solar%2C%20EVs%2C%20and%20batteries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-meeting-us-climate-solar-panels-coal-power-energy-security-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A