er-revenues-124050201035_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2252%2C%20Not%20223%20Sackings%2C%20Delhi%20Women's%20Panel%20Clarifies%20Amid%20Massive%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFifty-two%20and%20not%20223%20employees%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20or%20DCW%20have%20been%20terminated%2C%20clarified%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%20hours%20after%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%20announced%20the%20mass%20sackings%20which%20drew%20massive%20criticism%20from%20the%20former%20president%20of%20the%20city's%20women%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20order%20by%20Lt%20Governor%20Vinai%20Saxena's%20office%20stated%20the%20WCD%20had%20terminated%20the%20services%20of%20223%20contractual%20staff.%20However%2C%20a%20WCD%20official%20clarified%20that%20while%20223%20posts%20were%20%26quot%3Billegally%26quot%3B%20created%2C%20only%2052%20staff%20were%20hired%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20posts%20remained%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20DCW%20chief%20and%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%20termed%20it%20a%20%26quot%3BTughlaqi%26quot%3B%20order.%20Taking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20revision%20in%20the%20number%20of%20sacked%20employees%2C%20she%20said%20the%20numbers%20were%20reduced%20%26quot%3Bafter%20one%20press%20conference%20by%20me%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20the%20way%20government%20functions%3F%20Even%20by%20this%20calculation%2C%20only%2038%20staff%20shall%20remain%20in%20the%20Commission!%20How%20will%20Sahyogini%2C%20181%20women%20helpline%2C%20Rape%20Crisis%20Cell%2C%20Crisis%20Intervention%20Centre%2C%20Mahila%20Panchayats%2C%20Acid%20attack%20and%20rehabilitation%20cell%20function%20with%2038%20staff%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAfter%20one%20press%20conference%20by%20me%2C%20they%20have%20reduced%20the%20number%20of%20so%20called%20illegally%20appointed%20persons%20from%20223%20to%2052!%20Is%20this%20the%20way%20government%20functions%3F%20Even%20by%20this%20calculation%2C%20only%2038%20staff%20shall%20remain%20in%20the%20Commission!%20How%20will%20Sahyogini%2C%20181%20women%20helpline%2C%20Rape%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNhsuCw9woW%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNhsuCw9woW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Swati%20Maliwal%20(%40SwatiJaiHind)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSwatiJaiHind%2Fstatus%2F1785997807624532087%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20the%20department%20has%2090%20employees%20-%2082%20on%20contract%20and%20eight%20regular.%20After%20the%20sackings%2C%20only%2038%20remain%20in%20the%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20a%20Hindi%20post%20on%20X%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLG%20Saheb%20has%20issued%20a%20'Tughlaqi'%20order%20to%20remove%20all%20the%20contract%20staff%20of%20DCW.%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20a%20total%20of%2090%20staffers%20in%20the%20Women's%20Commission%2C%20out%20of%20which%20only%208%20people%20have%20been%20given%20by%20the%20government%2C%20the%20rest%20are%20on%20a%20contract%20for%203%20months%20each.%20If%20all%20the%20contract%20staff%20are%20removed%2C%20the%20Women's%20Commission%20will%20be%20locked.%20Why%20are%20these%20people%20doing%20this%3F%20This%20organisation%20is%20built%20with%20blood%20and%20sweat.%20Instead%20of%20giving%20it%20staff%20and%20protection%2C%20you%20are%20destroying%20it%20from%20the%20roots%3F%20As%20long%20as%20I%20am%20alive%2C%20I%20will%20not%20let%20the%20Women's%20Commission%20be%20closed.%20Put%20me%20in%20jail%2C%20don't%20oppress%20women!%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Maliwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20termination%20has%20been%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20report%20submitted%20by%20a%20committee%20in%20June%202017.%20It%20was%20constituted%20by%20former%20Lt%20Governor%20Anil%20Baijal%20to%20look%20into%20the%20complaints%20of%20%26quot%3Birregular%20and%20illegally%20created%20posts%20and%20contractual%20appointments%26quot%3B%20in%20February%2C%202017%20at%20DCW%2C%20said%20the%20statement%20from%20the%20WCD%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%20cites%20the%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20Act%20and%20says%20that%20the%20panel%20has%20a%20sanctioned%20strength%20of%2040%20employees%20and%20that%20223%20new%20posts%20were%20created%20without%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%20The%20order%20also%20states%20that%20the%20commission%20does%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20hire%20employees%20on%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20that%20the%20then%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Women%20Commission%2C%20Swati%20Maliwal%2C%20had%20made%20the%20appointments%20without%20permission%2C%20going%20against%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20April%2029%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDepartment%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(DWCD)%20vide%20letter%20dated%20October%205%2C%202016%20again%20informed%20DCW%20that%20the%20order%20issued%20by%20DCW%20dated%20September%2010%2C%202016%20had%20no%20approval%20of%20the%20Competent%20Authority%20i.e.%20Hon'ble%20Lt.%20Governor%20for%20creation%20of%20said%20223%20posts%20in%20DCW.%20As%20per%20sub-section%20(i)%20of%20section%2005%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20women%20Act%2C%202013%20which%20reads%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20shall%20provide%20the%20Commission%20with%20such%20officers%20and%20employees%20as%20may%20be%20necessary%20for%20the%20efficient%20performance%20of%20the%20functions%20of%20the%20Commission%20under%20this%20Act.%20Therefore%2C%20DCW%20doesn't%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20appoint%2Fengage%20the%20employees%20on%20its%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20further%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20appointments%20were%20done%20without%20the%20approval%20of%20a%20competent%20authority.%20It%20also%20mentioned%20that%20Ms%20Maliwal%20was%20advised%20repeatedly%20to%20seek%20the%20finance%20department's%20approval%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwati%20Maliwal%20headed%20the%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20for%20nine%20years%20before%20entering%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20The%20post%20of%20the%20panel's%20chairperson%20is%20currently%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714655340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmpcp72vs_swati-maliwal-pti_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F52-not-223-sackings-delhi-womens-panel-clarifies-amid-massive-row-5573348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fifty-two%20and%20not%20223%20employees%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20or%20DCW%20have%20been%20terminated%2C%20clarified%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%20hours%20after%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%20announced%20the%20mass%20sackings%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F52-not-223-sackings-delhi-womens-panel-clarifies-amid-massive-row-5573348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F52-not-223-sackings-delhi-womens-panel-clarifies-amid-massive-row-5573348%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F52-not-223-sackings-delhi-womens-panel-clarifies-amid-massive-row-5573348%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pro-Gaza%20stirs%3A%20US%20varsities%20contaminated%2C%20says%20Israel%20prez%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714655327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109789700%2Cimgsize-850787.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-president-says-