ven%20by%20the%20ministry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20nephew%20of%20former%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20over%20videos%20in%20which%20he%20can%20allegedly%20be%20seen%20sexually%20assaulting%20multiple%20women.%20The%20Hassan%20MP%20had%20left%20for%20Germany%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20voting%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20of%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20had%20begun%20circulating%20online%20the%20same%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Mr%20Revanna%20was%20travelling%20on%20a%20diplomatic%20passport%20and%20whether%20political%20clearance%20was%20given%20by%20the%20ministry%2C%20MEA%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20at%20the%20weekly%20media%20briefing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20political%20clearance%20was%20either%20sought%20from%20or%20issued%20by%20the%20MEA%20in%20respect%20of%20the%20travel%20of%20the%20said%20MP%20to%20Germany.%20Obviously%2C%20no%20visa%20note%20was%20issued%20either.%20No%20visa%20is%20required%20for%20diplomatic%20passport%20holders%20to%20travel%20to%20Germany.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ministry%20has%20also%20not%20issued%20any%20visa%20note%20for%20any%20other%20country%20for%20the%20said%20MP.%20He%20travelled%20on%20a%20diplomatic%20passport%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20had%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20asked%20for%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20passport%20of%20Mr%20Revanna%20and%20the%20initiation%20of%20other%20necessary%20steps%20to%20ensure%20his%20swift%20return.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20this%20and%20whether%20Mr%20Revanna%20has%20been%20located%20anywhere%20in%20Germany%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said%20a%20diplomatic%20passport%20can%20be%20revoked%20under%20the%20Passport%20Act%2C%201967.%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20the%20passport%20can%20be%20revoked%20based%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20a%20court.%20We%20have%20not%20received%20any%20such%20directions%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20another%20question%20on%20whether%20taking%20political%20clearance%20is%20mandatory%20while%20travelling%20on%20a%20diplomatic%20passport%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20only%20said%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20are%20entitled%20to%20such%20passports%20and%20that%20no%20political%20clearance%20was%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Karnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%20the%20suspended%20JDS%20leader%20has%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20investigating%20the%20sex%20scandal%20and%20also%20hinted%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-cops-reject-prajwal-revannas-request-for-time-to-join-sex-harassment-probe-5570589%5C%22%3Ecould%20be%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20he%20did%20not%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20slugfest%20over%20the%20issue%20has%20also%20escalated%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20attacking%20the%20JDS%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20inviting%20sharp%20retorts%20from%20both%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714653300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flmmnkp3g_prajwal-revanna_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-not-given-political-clearance-for-germany-visit-centre-5572952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20political%20row%20over%20sex%20scandal-accused%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20said%20that%20he%20travelled%20to%20Ge