egislative%20assemblies%20and%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20appalling%20actions%20by%20lawmakers%20raise%20significant%20concerns%20regarding%20women's%20safety%20and%20political%20parties'%20track%20records%20in%20selecting%20candidates%20for%20state%20and%20general%20elections.%20While%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20(JD-S)%20has%20suspended%20Prajwal%2C%20it%20now%20falls%20upon%20government%20authorities%20to%20repatriate%20him%20from%20abroad%20and%20charge%20him%20under%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDamage%20Control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Freporter-vlogs%2Fwhat-is-the-sex-scandal-that-forced-deve-gowda-s-grandson-to-leave-india-780034%5C%22%3EThis%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taken%20on%20a%20political%20dimension%2C%20with%20former%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20H.D.%20Kumaraswamy%20alleging%20a%20conspiracy%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20tarnish%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeve-gowdas-grandson-accused-in-sex-scandal-to-return-within-a-week-says-lawyer-5567440%5C%22%3EGowda%20family's%3C%2Fa%3E%20reputation%20just%20before%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20aiming%20to%20undermine%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2014%20seats%20in%20North%20Karnataka%20going%20to%20polls%20in%20Phase%203%20on%20May%207%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20asked%20why%20the%20tapes%20were%20released%20now%20when%20the%20Congress%20allegedly%20possessed%20them%20since%20December.%20He%20also%20held%20the%20Congress%20government%20responsible%20for%20Prajwal's%20reported%20flight%20to%20Germany%20after%20the%20April%2026%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-protect-him-says-hd-kumaraswamy-uncle-of-karnataka-mp-prajwal-revanna-in-video-scandal-5555096%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BWon't%20Protect%20Him%26quot%3B%3A%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20Uncle%20Of%20Karnataka%20MP%20In%20Video%20Scandal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%20accuses%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20campaigning%20for%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20BJP's%20alliance%20with%20the%20JD(S)%20despite%20these%20allegations%20and%20its%20commitment%20to%20women%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESign%20Of%20A%20Bigger%20Problem%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20once%20again%20brought%20into%20focus%20the%20use%20of%20muscle%20power%20in%20elections.%20According%20to%20a%202023%20analysis%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%2C%20out%20of%20the%204%2C809%20election%20affidavits%20of%20sitting%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%2C%20134%20individuals%2C%20including%2021%20MPs%20and%20113%20MLAs%2C%20have%20cases%20related%20to%20crimes%20against%20women.%20The%20BJP%20leads%20with%2044%20such%20members%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Congress%20with%2025%20and%20AAP%20with%2013.%20Alarmingly%2C%20as%20many%20as%2018%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20have%20declared%20pending%20cases%20related%20to%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-prajwal-revannas-ex-driver-bjp-leader-accuse-each-other-of-leaking-videos-5556892%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Prajwal%20Revanna's%20Ex%20Driver%2C%20BJP%20Leader%20Accuse%20Each%20Other%20Of%20Leaking%20Videos%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prevalence%20of%20such%20cases%2C%20including%20charges%20like%20assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20outrage%20modesty%2C%20reflects%20poorly%20on%20parties%20across%20the%20spectrum.%20It's%20alarming%20how%20candidates%20with%20criminal%20cases%20against%20them%20manage%20to%20win%20elections.%20This%20has%20been%20an%20ugly%20reality%20that%20no%20one%20has%20taken%20pains%20to%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20crucial%20demographic%20in%20elections%2C%20often%20considered%20%26quot%3Bkingmakers%26quot%3B%20and%20demonstrating%20higher%20turnout%20than%20men%20in%20many%20instances.%20However%2C%20incidents%20like%20these%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20episode%2C%20could%20lead%20to%20disillusionment%20among%20women%20voters%2C%20affecting%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrioritising%20Women%2C%20In%20Spirit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20despite%20the%20heavy%20rhetoric%20over%20women's%20representation%2C%20parties%20have%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20even%20half%20of%20the%20promised%2033%25%20quota%20for%20women%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20fielding%20candidates.%20This%20may%20negatively%20impact%20women's%20perception%20of%20politics%20and%20politicians%20at%20a%20time%20when%20their%20participation%20is%20increasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Parliament%20must%20enact%20stricter%20laws%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20should%20implement%20more%20stringent%20rules%20for%20candidate%20information%2C%20especially%20regarding%20criminal%20cases%2C%20to%20empower%20voters%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions.%20Parties%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20need%20to%20prioritise%20genuine%20concerns%20and%20respect%20for%20women's%20welfare%20over%20political%20gains%20and%20superficial%20gestures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20big%20ask.%20Now%20is%20the%20time%20for%20a%20much-needed%20cleanup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714652640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt