300-missiles-300-drones-3200-guided-bombs-in-april-against-ukraine-zelenskyy-says%2Farticleshow%2F109786909.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-used-300-missiles-300-drones-3200-guided-bombs-in-april-against-ukraine-zelenskyy-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F109786909.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-used-300-missiles-300-drones-3200-guided-bombs-in-april-against-ukraine-zelenskyy-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F109786909.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Meet%20To%20Discuss%20Amethi%2C%20Raebareli%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20are%20having%20a%20meeting%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20candidates%20for%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%2C%20where%20the%20last%20date%20for%20filing%20of%20nomination%20is%20Friday.%20The%20party%20had%20handed%20Mr%20Kharge%20the%20responsibility%20of%20choosing%20a%20candidate%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20two%20leaders%20are%20expected%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20decision%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20which%20is%20being%20held%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20gone%20for%20campaigning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20while%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20expected%20to%20contest%20on%20one%20seat%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20still%20remains%20firm%20on%20her%20decision%20not%20to%20contest%20despite%20much%20pressure.%20There%20was%20widespread%20expectation%20that%20she%20would%20step%20into%20her%20mother's%20shoes%20in%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20delaying%20the%20decision%20for%20weeks.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20time%20has%20almost%20run%20out.%20Two%20days%20ago%2C%20Congress%20workers%20went%20into%20protest%20mode%20in%20Amethi%2C%20seeking%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20as%20candidate.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20for%20both%20seats%20is%20due%20on%20May%2020%2C%20the%20fifth%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20reports%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20may%20not%20be%20interested%20in%20contesting%20from%20Amethi.%20A%20victory%20would%20mean%20that%20he%20might%20have%20to%20surrender%20the%20Kerala%20seat%2C%20which%20sent%20him%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20sources%20hinted%20that%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20reluctance%20stems%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20her%20victory%20from%20Raebareli%20would%20place%20all%20three%20Gandhi%20family%20members%20in%20parliament%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20BJP%20accusation%20of%20dynasty%20politics.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20till%20now%20represented%20Raebareli%2C%20has%20moved%20onto%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20feels%20much%20rides%20on%20the%20decision%20on%20these%20two%20key%20seats%20--%20the%20party%20expects%20it%20to%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20election.%20Polls%20on%20353%20seats%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20remaining%20five%20phases.%20Of%20these%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20contesting%20on%20330%20--%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20the%20Surat%20and%20Indore%20seats%20without%20a%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20lowest%20number%20of%20seats%20the%20Congress%20has%20contested%20in%20since%20Independence.%20The%20reason%20is%20the%20united%20front%20the%20Opposition%20is%20putting%20up%20and%20many%20of%20the%20seats%20have%20been%20conceded%20to%20allies%20in%20various%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714648920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fva0951pg_rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-mallikarjun-kharge-rahul-gandhi-meet-to-discuss-amethi-raebareli-5572293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20ar