20bring%20down%20the%20numbers%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%2C%20underscoring%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20parties%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20in%20alliance%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20know%20the%20context%20of%20what%20Adhir%20ji%20said%2C%20but%20we%20aim%20to%20reduce%20the%20numbers%20of%20BJP%20in%20West%20Bengal%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20won%2018%20out%20of%2042%20seats%2C%20we%20have%20to%20reduce%20their%20numbers%20and%20that%20is%20the%20only%20goal.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20assembly%20election%2C%20this%20is%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Congress%2C%20along%20with%20Left%20parties%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20TMC%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20also%20said%20they%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20though%20we%20are%20not%20in%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20holds%20Mr%20Chowdhury%2C%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20%C2%A0breakdown%20of%20seat-sharing%20discussions%20with%20Congress%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20said%20after%20acting%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Beyes%20and%20ears%20of%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20has%20now%20been%20promoted%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BListen%20to%20how%20the%20B-Team%20member%20is%20openly%20asking%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20-%20a%20party%20that%20refused%20to%20release%20Bengal's%20rightful%20dues%20and%20deprived%20our%20people%20of%20their%20rights.%20Only%20a%20Bangla-Birodhi%20can%20campaign%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20repeatedly%20insulted%20Bengal's%20icons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Tri