est's%20alleged%20relationship%20with%20the%20petitioner's%20wife.%20The%20defence%20counsel%20argued%20that%20the%20statement%20was%20made%20out%20of%20anguish%20upon%20discovering%20the%20alleged%20affair%2C%20and%20the%20priest's%20decision%20to%20end%20his%20life%20was%20influenced%20by%20the%20affair%20becoming%20known%20to%20others%2C%20rather%20than%20solely%20by%20the%20accused's%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposing%20counsel%20contended%20that%20the%20priest%20took%20his%20own%20life%20due%20to%20the%20accused's%20threatening%20language%20about%20exposing%20the%20affair.%20However%2C%20the%20single%20judge%20bench%2C%20drawing%20on%20precedents%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20emphasised%20that%20such%20statements%20alone%20might%20not%20constitute%20abetment%20to%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20acknowledged%20the%20multifaceted%20reasons%20behind%20the%20priest's%20suicide%2C%20including%20the%20alleged%20illicit%20relationship%20he%20had%20despite%20his%20role%20as%20a%20father%20and%20priest.%20Recognising%20the%20complexities%20of%20human%20psychology%2C%20the%20court%20underscored%20the%20challenge%20of%20deciphering%20the%20human%20mind%20and%20declined%20to%20categorise%20the%20accused's%20statement%20as%20abetment%20to%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20the%20court%20quashed%20the%20case%2C%20emphasising%20the%20intricate%20nature%20of%20human%20behaviour%20and%20the%20inability%20to%20fully%20unravel%20the%20motivations%20behind%20such%20tragic%20incidents.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2