rged%20to%20take%20precautions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2014-15%2C%20extreme%20rainfall%20battered%20regions%20of%20the%20Arabian%20Peninsula%2C%20with%20Dubai%20experiencing%20the%20heaviest%20rains%20on%20record%20since%201949.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubai-based%20Emirates%20airline%20announced%20the%20cancellation%20of%20several%20flights%20on%20Thursday%20due%20to%20bad%20weather%20across%20the%20UAE%20as%20movements%20at%20Dubai%20International%20Airport%20(DXB)%20were%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20arriving%20or%20departing%20from%20Dubai%20airport%20on%202%20May%20can%20expect%20some%20delays%20as%20flights%20are%20rescheduled%2C%26quot%3B%20Emirates%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20flights%20have%20been%20cancelled%20on%20May%202%3A%20EK%20123%2F124%20-%20between%20Dubai%20and%20Istanbul%2C%20EK%20763%2F764%20-%20between%20Dubai%20and%20Johannesburg%2C%20EK%20719%2F720%20-%20between%20Dubai%20and%20Nairobi%2C%20Ek%20921%2F922%20-%20between%20Dubai%20and%20Cairo%2C%20EK%20903%2F904%20-%20between%20Dubai%20and%20Amman%2C%20and%20EK%20352%2F353%20-%20between%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore%20(EK353%20departing%203%20May%2C%2012.30%20am%20-%20UAE%20time).%20The%20airline%20has%20also%20waived%20rebooking%20charges%20to%20help%20stranded%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20expected%20weather%20conditions%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%20recommended%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20NCEMA%2C%20activating%20remote%20learning%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%20for%20all%20educational%20institutions%2C%20with%20decisions%20to%20be%20made%20by%20the%20competent%20authorities%20at%20the%20federal%20level%20and%20officials%20of%20local%20emergency%20management%20teams%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20and%20the%20Emirates%20Schools%20Establishment%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20heavy%20winds%20and%20light%20rains%20lashed%20across%20the%20main%20cities%2C%20residents%20appeared%20more%20equipped%20to%20ride%20it%20out.%20Remote%20work%20systems%20were%20advised%20for%20all%20government%20and%20private%20sectors%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%2C%20except%20for%20vital%20jobs%20that%20require%20presence%20at%20the%20workplace%20and%20those%20involved%20in%20response%20and%20recovery%20efforts.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20NCEMA%2C%20also%20decided%20to%20close%20all%20roads%20leading%20to%20areas%20prone%20to%20flash%20floods%2C%20water%20accumulations%2C%20and%20dams%20during%20the%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20urged%20the%20public%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20these%20areas%20and%20adhere%20to%20safety%20standards%20and%20guidelines%2C%20avoid%20mountainous%2C%20desert%2C%20and%20coastal%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20statement.%20Besides%20moderate%20to%20heavy%20rain%20in%20scattered%20areas%2C%20accompanied%20by%20occasional%20lightning%20and%20thunder%2C%20a%20possibility%20of%20small%20hail%2C%20concentrated%20in%20the%20western%20regions%2C%20on%20the%20coasts%2C%20and%20in%20some%20eastern%20areas%20have%20also%20been%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20flights%20were%20disrupted%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20some%20events%20were%20postponed%20due%20to%20the%20inclement%20weather%20conditions.%20Abu%20Dhabi-based%20Etihad%20Airways%20said%20its%20flight%20(EY197)%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Abu%20Dhabi%20Zayed%20International%20Airport%20(AUH)%20was%20diverted%20to%20Al-Ain%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%26quot%3B%20The%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20to%20arrive%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20around%201.35%20pm%2C%20eventually%20landed%20around%207-30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Dubai%2C%20the%20Ports%2C%20Customs%2C%20and%20Free%20Zone%20Corporation%20(PCFC)%20announced%20the%20temporary%20suspension%20of%20accepting%20requests%20for%20the%20entry%20and%20departure%20of%20wooden%20dhows%20in%20Dubai.%20The%20PCFC%20has%20also%20advised%20sailors%20to%20avoid%20sailing%20during%20this%20time%20to%20ensure%20everyone's%20safety.%20As%20dark%20clouds%20gathered%20and%20howling%20winds%20started%20to%20beat%20the%20windows%20across%20the%20city%2C%20residents%20looked%20more%20assured%2C%20and%20definitely%20better%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubai%20Metro%20announced%20the%20extension%20of%20operating%20hours%20ahead%20of%20expected%20weather%20conditions%2C%20extending%20from%2012%20am%20to%205%20am%20(the%20next%20day).%20However%2C%20the%20number%20of%20stops%20for%20these%20trains%20was%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHeavy%20thunderstorms%20are%20forecast%20in%20Dubai%20on%20May%202.%20If%20you're%20travelling%20to%20Dubai%20International%20Airport%2C%20you%20may%20experience%20road%20delays.%20We%20recommend%20adding%20extra%20travel%20time%20to%20reach%20the%20airport%20and%20using%20Dubai%20Metro%20where%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Emirates%20airline's%20spokesperson%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20local%20media%20as%20saying%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20have%20also%20been%20advised%20not%20to%20sail%2C%20and%20avoid%20valley%20areas%2C%20torrential%20rains%2C%20and%20low-lying%20places.%20They%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20exercise%20caution%20while%20driving%20vehicles%20and%20adhere%20to%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20competent%20authorities.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714641300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhcudrh98_dubai-rain-afp_625x300_17_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuae-weather-today-several-flights-cancelled-as-heavy-rains-thunderstorms-return-to-uae-5570795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heav