a.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20Revanna's%20obscene%20video%20showing%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20of%20women%20has%20taken%20the%20political%20circles%20in%20Karnataka%20by%20storm%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20sources%20stated%20that%20the%20sitting%20MP%20and%20NDA%20candidate%20from%20Hassan%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20time%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20is%20expected%20to%20arrive%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20May%2015%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20his%20request%20yet%20and%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20was%20expected%20to%20land%20in%20Bengaluru%20from%20Frankfurt%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20development%2C%20the%20former%20driver%20of%20accused%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20who%20had%20confessed%20that%20he%20had%20given%20the%20pen%20drive%20with%20the%20videos%20of%20the%20JD(S)%20leader%20sexually%20abusing%20women%2C%20to%20BJP%20leader%20Devaraje%20Gowda%2C%20has%20disappeared%20following%20a%20SIT%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20Karthik%20had%20worked%20with%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20for%2013%20years%20and%20had%20fallen%20out%20with%20him%20a%20year%20ago%20over%20an%20alleged%20land%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20is%20alleging%20that%20some%20influential%20leaders%20are%20behind%20the%20driver's%20disappearance%20thereby%20alluding%20to%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivakumar%20and%20questioned%20who%20sent%20Karthik%20to%20Malaysia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Dy%20CM%20Shivakumar%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20brother%20saying%20so%3F%20That%20means%20he%20knows%20everything.%20Let%20him%20get%20the%20information%20from%20the%20central%20government.%20I%20am%20not%20crazy%20to%20send%20him%20(Karthik)%20abroad.%20I%20am%20a%20street%20fighter.%20There%20is%20no%20necessity%20for%20me%20to%20carry%20out%20politics%20by%20hiding%20people.%20They%20(Deve%20Gowda%20family)%20need%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20boy%20(Karthik)%20had%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20given%20the%20pen%20drive%20containing%20obscene%20videos%20of%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20to%20BJP%20leaders.%20Let%20the%20discussion%20on%20release%20of%20the%20pen%20drive%20take%20place%20later.%20Let's%20not%20divert%20from%20the%20real%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%2C%20R%20Ashoka's%20demand%20for%20the%20government%20to%20vacate%20the%20seat%20of%20power%20if%20it%20is%20incapable%20of%20arresting%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20Dy%20CM%20Shivakumar%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CAshoka%20is%20in%20a%20constitutional%20position.%20He%20was%20raising%20his%20voice%20in%20other%20issues%20and%20regarding%20this%20case%20he%20is%20not%20opening%20his%20mouth.%20He%20should%20take%20state%20BJP%20President%2C%20BY%20Vijayendra%20and%20others%20and%20meet%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20video%20scandal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20should%20assure%20them%20of%20justice%20and%20give%20courage%20to%20them.%20Former%20PM%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20former%20CM%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20who%20claim%20to%20have%20respect%20for%20women%2C%20should%20meet%20the%20victims%20by%20going%20to%20their%20homes.%20Why%20are%20they%20not%20doing%20so%3F%E2%80%9D%20Dy%20CM%20Shivakumar%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20urging%20him%20to%20cancel%20the%20diplomatic%20passport%20of%20Prajwal%20Revanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20suspended%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20formed%20the%20SIT%20to%20probe%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%20on%20Wednesday%20commented%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20the%20issue%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CTruth%20will%20prevail%20soon.%20I%20am%20not%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20attend%20the%20enquiry.%20I%20have%20communicated%20to%20CID%2C%20Bengaluru%20through%20my%20advocate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20social%20media%20post%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20sought%20seven%20days%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20SIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714640400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flmmnkp3g_prajwal-revanna_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-driver-who-leaked-sex-tapes-goes-missing-amid-probe-5571371%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20political%20slugfest%20in%20Karnataka%20over%20the%20obscene%20video%20scandal%20involving%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowdas%20grandson%20and%20suspended%20JD(S)%20leader%20Prajwal%20Revanna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-driver-who-leaked-sex-tapes-goes-missing-amid-probe-5571371%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-driver-who-leaked-sex-tapes-goes-missing-amid-probe-5571371%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-driver-who-leaked-sex-tapes-goes-missing-amid-probe-5571371%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20using%20choking%20agents%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20US%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714640151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2A8F%2Fproduction%2F_133259801_7f328f239c84982c35a64bd681bf21089985fc8e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68941220%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2