0solution%20for%20diarrhoea%20and%20dehydration%2C%20especially%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfants%20and%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Indian%20households%20are%20stocked%20up%20with%20packets%20of%20ORS%20solutions%2C%20and%20use%20them%20to%20beat%20the%20heat%2C%20also%20using%20it%20for%20children.%20Pharmacies%20are%20also%20stocked%20up%20with%20ORS%20solutions%20from%20different%20brands%2C%20available%20in%20different%20flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20bone%20of%20contention%20here%20is%2C%20are%20these%20real%20ORS%20solutions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20ORS%20solution%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20getting%20into%20identifying%20what%E2%80%99s%20real%20and%20not%2C%20we%20first%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20purpose%20behind%20the%20creation%20of%20this%20life-saving%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20WHO%2C%20diarrhoea%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20in%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20five.%20Deaths%20due%20to%20diarrhoea%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoccur%20due%20to%20dehydration%2C%20which%20can%20be%20prevented%20by%20giving%20fluids%20at%20home%2C%20and%20in%20severe%20cases%2C%20ORS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EORS%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20salt%20and%20sugar%20dissolved%20in%20water%20that%20can%20treat%20dehydration%20caused%20by%20diarrhoea%2C%20heat%20stroke%20or%20other%20illnesses%20where%20you%20lose%20a%20lot%20of%20fluid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsed%20since%201969%20by%20the%20WHO%20and%20UNICEF%2C%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20treatments%20for%20clinical%20dehydration%20across%20the%20world%2C%20which%20is%20cheap%20on%20the%20pocket%20too.%20It%20is%20recommended%20to%20treat%20dehydration%2