EIn%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20Manoj%20Sanker%20saw%20his%20parents%20go%20through%20a%20similar%20trial%20when%20their%20second%20son%20was%20born%20premature.%20He%20recounts%20seeing%20his%20middle%20class%20family%20going%20above%20and%20beyond%20to%20ensure%20that%20he%20got%20the%20best%20treatment.%20Years%20later%2C%20when%2032-year-old%20Manoj%20had%20to%20think%20of%20a%20startup%20idea%20in%20healthcare%2C%20neonatal%20care%20was%20his%20first%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratyusha%20Pareddy%20hails%20from%20a%20family%20of%20doctors%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20household%20where%20healthcare%20was%20dinner%20table%20conversation.%20After%20completing%20her%20engineering%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20did%20a%20masters%20degree%20in%20Industrial%20and%20Product%20Design%20from%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20project%20at%20NID%2C%20she%20learnt%20about%20how%20design%20could%20transcend%20beyond%20aesthetics%20and%20be%20used%20to%20create%20a%20difference.%20She%20wanted%20to%20use%20her%20designs%20to%20create%20impact%20and%20improve%20lives%20at%20the%20grassroot%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20shared%20a%20common%20vision%20of%20using%20technology%20and%20design%20to%20build%20solutions%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20population%2C%20i.e.%20babies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fnemocare-min-1713946003.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manoj%20and%20Pratyusha%2C%20Founders%20of%20Nemocare%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fnemocare-min-1713946003.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fnemocare-min-1713946003-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fnemocare-min-1713946003-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fnemocare-min-1713946003-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fnemocare-min-1713946003-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManoj%20and%20Pratyusha%2C%20Founders%20of%20Nemocare%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20engineers%20launched%20Raksha%2C%20a%20wearable%20device%20that%20monitors%20vital%20parameters%20of%20a%20newborn%20and%20helps%20nurses%20and%20doctors%20provide%20timely%20intervention%20through%20their%20medtech%20startup%20NemoCare%20Wellness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202022%2C%20this%20device%20has%20helped%20over%2020%2C000%20newborns%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOn%20a%20mission%20to%20reduce%20newborn%20mortality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20released%20a%20report%20called%20%E2%80%98Born%20Too%20Soon%3A%20Decade%20of%20action%E2%80%99%20in%20May%202023.%20According%20to%20this%20report%2C%20India%20recorded%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20preterm%20births%20%E2%80%94%203.2%20million%20%E2%80%94%20in%202020.%20Almost%201%20in%2010%20babies%20born%20is%20preterm%2C%20and%20the%20neonatal%20mortality%20rate%20is%2024.9%20per%201%2C000%20live%20births%2C%20according%20to%20NFHS-5%20(2019-21).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20to%20improve%20newborn%20survival%20is%20to%20provide%20essential%20newborn%20care%20to%20identify%20and%20treat%20high%20risk%20newborns.%20This%20includes%20early%20initiation%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255089%2Fdr-m-aishwarya-coimbatore-parenting-network-tamil-nadu-taboo-how-to-donate-breast-milk-feeding-awareness-taboo-myths-banks-postpartum-depression-covid-19-pandemic-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreastfeeding%2C%20skin-to-skin%20contact%3C%2Fa%3E%20(kangaroo%20mother%20care)%2C%20timely%20intervention%2C%20facilities%20with%20special%20newborn%20care%20units%2C%20amongst%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gap%20which%20Pratyusha%20and%20Manoj%20found%20during%20their%20fellowship%20in%202016%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Healthcare%20Entrepreneurship%2C%20IIT-Hyderabad%2C%20was%20in%20neonatal%20care%2C%20particularly%20in%20their%20monitoring%20devices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20impactful%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280422%2Fbengaluru-entrepreneur-innovates-neonatal-device-hypthermia-newborns-bampu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20newborns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20are%20the%20most%20vulnerable.%20We%20felt%20that%20technology%20and%20support%20could%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20this%20segment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manoj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20a%20detailed%20six%20month%20clinical%20immersion%20where%20they%20shadowed%20doctors%20and%20visited%20different%20hospitals%20in%20Telangana%20during%20their%20fellowship.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20immersion%20process%2C%20we%20tried%20to%20understand%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20gauge%20the%20gaps%20in%20the%20system.%20We%20came%20across%20several%20premature%20babies%20who%20were%20super%20vulnerable.%20There%20was%20an%20acute%20shortage%20of%20monitoring%20devices%20or%20any%20kind%20of%20support%20mechanisms%20for%20the%20nursing%20staff%20and%20the%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20government%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manoj%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20field%20visits%2C%20the%20duo%20spoke%20to%20various%20stakeholders%20and%20worked%20on%20building%20a%20solution%20with%20their%20expertise%20in%20engineering%20and%20design.%20While%20there%20was%20an%20acute%20gap%20of%20monitoring%20devices%2C%20the%20infrastructure%20where%20such%20a%20solution%20could%20be%20implemented%20was%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20immediately%20started%20building%20their%20solution%2C%20and%20the%20first%20prototype%20of%20Raksha%20was%20ready%20and%20tested%20before%20they%20even%20graduated%20in%202017.%20They%20followed%20it%20up%20by%20launching%20Nemocare%20Wellness%20in%20July%202017.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20device%20that%20can%20save%20a%20newborn%E2%80%99s%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NemoCare%20Raksha%20device%20is%20fitted%20on%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20foot%20like%20a%20smart%20sock%2C%20explains%20Manoj.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201007px)%20100vw%2C%201007px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNemocare-device-on-baby-1713946483.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221007%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20smart%20sock%20that%20can%20save%20lives%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNemocare-device-on-baby-1713946483.jpg%201007w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNemocare-device-on-baby-1713946483-300x218.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNemocare-device-on-baby-1713946483-500x364.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNemocare-device-on-baby-1713946483-768x559.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNemocare-device-on-baby-1713946483-150x109.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348116%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20smart%20sock%20that%20can%20save%20lives%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20device%20captures%20vital%20parameters%20of%20the%20baby%2C%20the%20heart%20rate%2C%20respiration%20rate%2C%20body%20oxygenation%20and%20body%20temperature.%20Other%20key%20vitals%20that%20help%20a%20doctor%2C%20including%20the%20heart%20rate%20variability%20and%20perfusion%20index%2C%20are%20also%20tracked.%20These%20help%20a%20doctor%2Fnurse%20identify%20if%20a%20baby%20is%20doing%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Manoj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20device%20is%20connected%20wirelessly%20to%20a%20central%20platform%20that%20helps%20a%20nurse%20monitor%20babies%20and%20alerts%20when%20a%20baby%20is%20distressed.%20This%20information%20is%20paired%20with%20a%20tablet%20or%20dashboard%20through%20an%20application.%20The%20entire%20set%20up%20of%20the%20device%2C%20including%20a%20bedside%20tablet%2C%20training%20is%20given%20by%20the%20company.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20vital%20information%20is%20relayed%20on%20the%20display%20and%20pushed%20on%20the%20cloud%20and%20central%20monitor%20which%20helps%20a%20healthcare%20provider%20monitor%2040-50%20babies%20in%20one%20shot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20solves%20the%20problem%20faced%20in%20most%20government%20and%20smaller%20hospitals%20of%20resource%20constraints%20and%20also%20helps%20in%20remote%20patient%20monitoring.%20It%20provides%20ICU%20grade%20monitoring%20even%20when%20the%20baby%20is%20with%20the%20mother%2C%20providing%20an%20advantage%20of%20Kangaroo%20mother%20care%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20initial%20grants%20from%20the%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20the%20entrepreneurs%20started%20testing%20their%20products%20and%20developed%20different%20prototypes%20over%204.5%20years%2C%20before%20they%20launched%20the%20final%20product%2018%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20conducted%20initial%20studies%20at%20private%20hospitals%20like%20AIG%20Hospital%2C%20Kamineni%20Hospitals%2C%20and%20at%20government%20hospitals%20like%20Niloufer%20Hospital%20in%20Hyderabad.%20After%20this%2C%20they%20tested%20their%20device%20in%20hospitals%20across%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20product%20provides%20every%20baby%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328138%2Fmadurai-dr-swaminathan-doctor-on-wheels-takes-affordable-healthcare-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eright%20treatment%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20the%20right%20time%20across%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20is%20that%20whenever%20babies%20across%20the%20world%2C%20despite%20their%20economic%20status%20and%20background%2C%20need%20healthcare%2C%20our%20device%20should%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20the%20right%20intervention.%20It%20should%20reach%20all%20hospitals%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pratyusha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20founders%20have%20identified%20three%20avenues%20of%20sale.%20The%20first%20is%20to%20government%20settings%20through%20CSR%20(Corporate%20social%20responsibility)%2C%20second%20to%20small%20and%20mid-sized%20nursing%20homes%2C%20and%20the%20third%20to%20large%20private%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20government%20hospitals%2C%20we%20provide%20a%20bundle%20of%20products%2C%20which%20include%20five%20devices%2C%20chargers%2C%20a%20tablet%20for%20each%20device%2C%20and%20a%20central%20monitor%20if%20the%20hospital%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20one%20already.%20If%20they%20have%20a%20monitor%2C%20we%20share%20the%20credentials%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20see%20the%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Manoj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmall%20and%20medium-sized%20nursing%20homes%20aren%E2%80%99t%20charged%20for%20the%20device%2C%20but%20for%20every%20baby%20monitored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20hospitals%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20for%20the%20device%2C%20but%20charge%20the%20patient%20Rs%20600%20per%20baby.%20The%20patch%2C%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20changed%20once%20every%202-3%20days%2C%20costs%20Rs%20200.%20The%20hospitals%20charge%20the%20patients%20as%20per%20their%20paying%20capacity%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20less%20than%2010%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20delivery%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Manoj%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20device%20can%20be%20used%20for%20up%20to%20200%20times%20in%20a%20year%2C%20is%20rechargeable%2C%20reusable%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20patch%20that%20keeps%20it%20clean.%C2%A0%20Each%20baby%20gets%20a%20new%20patch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20large%20corporate%20hospitals%20and%20boutique%20maternal%20and%20child%20care%20centres%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20charge%20the%20entire%20cost%20per%20device.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20helped%20monitor%20over%2020%2C000%20neonates%20and%20possibly%20saved%20their%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20are%20now%20working%20on%20building%20an%20AI%20platform%20for%20neonatal%20units%2C%20with%20grants%20from%20BIRAC%20(Biotechnology%20Industry%20Research%20Assistance%20Council)%20%2C%20ICMR%20(Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%C2%A0%20Department).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20platform%20will%20help%20predict%20when%20a%20newborn%20is%20going%20to%20fall%20sick%20and%20any%20long%20term%20complications%20he%2Fshe%20may%20face.%20While%20the%20wearable%20is%20a%20real%20time%20problem%20solving%20device%2C%20the%20platform%20will%20talk%20about%20trends%20and%20the%20future%20health%20of%20the%20baby%2C%20predicting%20whatever%20is%20done%20manually%20today.%20It%20will%20also%20work%20as%20a%20decision%20support%20tool%20for%20doctors%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manoj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENemoCare%20Raksha%20also%20has%20plans%20of%20going%20global.%20The%20founders%20have%20applied%20for%20a%20US%20FDA%20approval%20as%20well..%20The%20device%20has%20two%20granted%20Indian%20patents%20and%20a%20US%20patent%20around%20business%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20plan%20to%20use%20our%20global%20profits%20to%20save%20babies%20in%20India.%20For%20every%20device%20sold%20to%20a%20western%20audience%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20invest%20%245in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manoj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20their%20fundraising%20for%20their%20AI%20platform%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%201%20crore%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20from%20Aman%20Gupta.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nemocare%20raised%20Rs%201%20Crore%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600-1536x1023.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAman-Gupt-aShark-Tank-Nemocare-Cheque-1713944600-272x182.jpg%20272w%5C%22