%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDisinherit%20him%20from%20the%20property.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20Bhavesh%20Kumar%20grew%20up%20hearing%20these%20comments%20from%20family%20members.%20Like%20most%20youths%2C%20the%20biggest%20question%20that%20was%20in%20front%20of%20him%20after%20he%20cleared%20class%2012%20was%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20you%20do%20next%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20his%20father%20who%20served%20in%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%2C%20Bhavesh%20was%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20defence%20forces%20or%20secure%20a%20well-paying%20government%20job.%20Contrarily%2C%20he%20aspired%20to%20start%20his%20own%20business.%20Initially%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20crack%20government%20exams%20but%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20his%20peers%20succeeded%2C%20he%20was%20jobless%20and%20clueless%20about%20what%20to%20do%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20has%20established%20a%20multi-crore%20business%20called%20Kasutam%20%E2%80%93%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269934%2Fbilona-ghee-homemade-recipe-order-online-punjab-woman-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA2%20%3Cem%3Eghee%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebrand%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20he%20sells%20freshly%20prepared%20ghee%20(clarified%20butter)%20at%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtoTyCaNxX-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtoTyCaNxX-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%