%3Ekhali%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder.%20Place%20a%20thin%20layer%20of%20soil%20above%20this%20and%20then%20water%20the%20soil.%20This%20will%20help%20you%20get%20good-sized%20fruits%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%E2%80%99s%20techniques%20have%20helped%20her%20get%20sufficient%20fruits%20for%20the%20past%20three%20decades.%20She%20now%20eagerly%20awaits%20to%20harvest%20mangoes%20from%20her%20garden!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20homemaker%2C%20gardening%20is%20more%20than%20a%20fun%20hobby.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20brings%20me%20immense%20mental%20peace%20and%20contentment.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20my%20everyday%20routine.%20My%20entire%20day%20goes%20by%20taking%20care%20of%20their%20nutrients%20and%20protecting%20them%20from%20diseases%20and%20pests.%20I%20raise%20these%20trees%20like%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Jayanti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Jayanti%20Sahoo.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714111642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FJayanti-Sahoo-4-1713363464.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Odisha's%20Jayanti%20Sahoo%20grows%2017%20types%20of%20fruits%20including%20guavas%2C%20pomegranates%2C%20oranges%2C%20white%20jamun%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20chikoos%20on%20her%20350%20sq%20ft%20terrace%20garden.%20With%20her%20eight%20secret%20tips%20and%20techniques%2C%20you%20too%20can%20grow%20fruits%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20Just%20Rs%20100%2C%20Donate%20A%20Pair%20of%20Slippers%20%26amp%3B%20Help%20Mirzapur%20Labourers%20Survive%20Scor